{"tid":1010202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地年初一電影票房破紀錄　國產科幻CG電影受注目","createTime":"2019-02-05T19:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T04:12:00.000Z","uid":117200,"like":5,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed94b211375c17a64ab106be845d9077ac0e044","tid":1010202,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T19:08:02.000Z","msg":"由北京上海等CG科技業界龍頭共同打做的重頭作《流浪地球》，在內地年初一的電影票房估計超過14億元人民幣，打破紀錄，兩齣國產科幻電影受注目。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/l/public/p2545553064.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg3.doubanio.com%2Fview%2Fphoto%2Fl%2Fpublic%2Fp2545553064.webp&h=691ba02f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《新華社》報道，首映的《流浪地球》公映前已經被認為是「中國電影產業現代化進程中真正意義上的科幻大片」，另一齣屬喜劇的《瘋狂的外星人》亦出現逆襲，令外界熱議2019年能否成為「中國科幻電影元年」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/l/public/p2541562055.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg3.doubanio.com%2Fview%2Fphoto%2Fl%2Fpublic%2Fp2541562055.webp&h=39444aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《流浪地球》影評<br />\n太陽即將毀滅，人類在地球表面建造出巨大的推進器，尋找新家園。然而宇宙之路危機四伏，為了拯救地球，為了人類能在漫長的2500年後抵達新的家園，流浪地球時代的年輕人挺身而出，展開爭分奪秒的生死之戰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/l/public/p2509014037.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.doubanio.com%2Fview%2Fphoto%2Fl%2Fpublic%2Fp2509014037.webp&h=14b20cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n預告<br />\n<a href=\"http://vt1.doubanio.com/201902060257/94b9306d277301c795b9b715197a40db/view/movie/M/402420330.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvt1.doubanio.com%2F201902060257%2F94b9306d277301c795b9b715197a40db%2Fview%2Fmovie%2FM%2F402420330.mp4&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=6a30ed1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://vt1.doubanio.com/201902060257/94b9306d277301c795b9b715197a40db/view/movie/M/402420330.mp4</a>"},{"pid":"0a1569b91f8bbaf98e5752c8bf2c7727451a471f","tid":1010202,"uid":117200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":